There is possible to concentrate into playing game by leaving counting for machine.

Key features of the counter:
 - scoring up to 11 or to 21 (two scores difference is required for win);
 - user can select (or randomize) who will serve first, then the app will calculate who serves and will display it;
 - counting is displayed with large font in landscape orientations, herewith tap area for adding score will be almost half of screen;
 - special mode that allows scoring with volume buttons, the app speaks current state (scores, who serves); so, device can be located in a pocket;
 - recording detailed history of played games (user can view it in the app, and also can copy it to computer via iTunes);
 - user can undo activities.

Some features are unavailable with iOS 6.x and below.

Two Devices Mode is in development.
